         <abstract id="aspace_8433a5a903e7db0b7fd699243026b74c">The Thomas Nast Collection documents satirical political illustrations drawn by Nast and published in newspapers and other serial publications in the late 19th century. The publications represented include <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>Harper's Weekly</part>
            </title>, the <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>New York Illustrated News</part>
            </title>, and the <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>Evening Post</part>
            </title>.</abstract>
